column16: Will Middlebrooks grounds into a double play, shortstop Ryan Flaherty to second baseman Jonathan Schoop to first baseman Dan Johnson.   Xander Bogaerts out at 2nd.
Xander Bogaerts singles on a line drive to left fielder Nate McLouth.
Ryan Lavarnway pops out to second baseman Jonathan Schoop.
Jonny Gomes homers (13) on a fly ball to left field.
Daniel Nava grounds into a force out, third baseman Ryan Flaherty to second baseman Jonathan Schoop.   Brandon Snyder out at 2nd.
David Ortiz homers (30) on a fly ball to left field.   Jackie Bradley Jr.   scores.    Dustin Pedroia scores.
